alt: Photo by MUJI Malaysia on October 21, 2024.
caption:
Dear valued customers,

We’ve received multiple reports of individuals impersonating the MUJI recruitment team and sending direct messages to customers with unauthorized and unverified job offers. 

These messages are part of phishing scams and are not affiliated with MUJI in any way. Often, they request a money deposit for the job or contain suspicious links that may lead to malware-infected websites.

As a precautionary measure, please avoid clicking on any links from unfamiliar or suspicious messages claiming to be from MUJI. If you’re interested in joining our team, visit muji.com/my/ and click under the Career tab for more information.

If you receive any suspicious emails/messages claiming to be from MUJI Malaysia, please forward them to customerservice@muji.com.my for verification. 

We kindly ask all customers to exercise caution and refrain from sharing personal information or clicking on any suspicious links. 

Be assured that we are actively addressing this issue to ensure the safety of our community.

caption:
✨ Celebrate Chinese New Year with MUJI! ✨

Have you cleaned your house for CNY yet? 🏠✨ Let’s welcome the Year of the Snake 🐍 with a sparkling clean home! 🎉 We’re giving away 10 Recycled Polypropylene Mop & Bucket Sets to help you prep for the festivities effortlessly! 🌟

𝐆𝐢𝐯𝐞𝐚𝐰𝐚𝐲 𝐩𝐞𝐫𝐢𝐨𝐝:
10/1/2025 - 02/02/2025

🧧 𝐇𝐨𝐰 𝐭𝐨 𝐩𝐚𝐫𝐭𝐢𝐜𝐢𝐩𝐚𝐭𝐞:
1️⃣ Like/Follow MUJI Malaysia’s Instagram (@mujimy) & Facebook (MUJI Malaysia)
2️⃣ Tag 3 friends in the comments.
3️⃣ Share this post to your Instagram Story or Facebook Feed.

*T&Cs Apply.
[1] Giveaway closes on 02/02/2025, 23:59, and winners will be announced on 14 February 2025.
[2] Open to all residents of Malaysia only.
[3] 10 Recycled Polypropylene Mop & Bucket Sets worth a total of RM1299 will be given away.
[4] One entry per participant, with each winner receiving one (1) MUJI Recycled Polypropylene Mop & Bucket Set. Winners are requested to contact us after the winner announcement have made.
[5] Winners are requested to self pick up from the nearest MUJI store with the pickup point options.
[6] All qualified winners will be picked randomly; entries not complete or not adhering to the rules may be disqualified.
[7]Prizes are non-refundable, non-exchangeable, not redeemable for cash, and non-transferable.
[8]Any prize not claimed within 5 days of notification will be forfeited.
[9] All winners chosen are final and at the sole discretion of MUJI Malaysia.
[10] MUJI Malaysia reserves the right to change or modify any terms & conditions at any time without prior notice.
[11] Winners must present evidence of completing all required steps when contacted.

Join now and start the year fresh and clean! 🏮✨

alt: Photo by MUJI Malaysia on December 31, 2024. Pode ser uma imagem de revista.
caption:
✨ 1 more hours to 2025, and our hearts are filled with gratitude as we reflect on 2024. ✨

This year, we proudly ventured into a new chapter with two store openings in Penang, expanded and relocated two existing MUJI stores, and unveiled our biggest store yet at MUJI Sunway Pyramid. We also introduced our first-ever gelato counters at MUJI Mid Valley.

Along with 773 new items launched throughout the year, including halal-certified snacks that brought even more choices to our customers, we’ve introduced products that truly won hearts.

None of this would have been possible without our dedicated team and the unwavering support of our MUJI friends and each of you. ❤️ Your trust, encouragement, and feedback have been our guiding light through every step of this journey.

As we turn the page to 2025, we look forward to creating even more meaningful moments with you. Here’s to another year of growth, connection, and shared memories. Thank you for making 2024 so special! 🌟

Bye bye 2024, see you in 2025!

Thank you for waiting and believing in us. ❤️‍🔥After opening our first store in Sunway Carnival Mall earlier this year, we are thrilled to finally be closer to everyone on the island. 🏝️ 

Drop by MUJI Gurney Plaza to explore a wide range of MUJI products thoughtfully designed to complement your daily life. Don’t miss out on our opening specials, available until 15 December 2024. 

We look forward to welcoming you!
